getReviewsAsRolesInStates runs the following query:

{code:sql}
select count(distinct review.id) from Review review join review.participants auth join review.participants mod join review.participants rev where (review.stateName = 'Review' or review.stateName = 'Summarize' ) and ( auth.author = true and auth.user = :auth or mod.moderator = true and mod.user = :mod or review.creator = :creator or rev.reviewer = true and rev.user = :rev ) 
{code}


Which can take 7+ minutes to complete for certain customers. 

These dbs are not particular large either:

{code:sql}
select count(*) from CRU_REVIEW_PARTICIPANT;
select count(*) from CRU_REVIEW;
{code}

returns 1619 and 268 for one particular customer suffering from the issue.

